2ï¸âƒ£ Bridge Design Pattern Kya Karta Hai?

Bridge pattern:

Separates abstraction (What) from implementation (How)
So that both can vary independently.

ğŸ’¡ Golden Line (Interview Me Bolne Layak)

Bridge pattern separates â€œWhat to be doneâ€ from â€œHow it is doneâ€ to avoid combinatorial explosion and make code scalable and maintainable.


3ï¸âƒ£ Structure of Bridge Pattern

Bridge me 4 main cheeze hoti hain:

Abstraction â†’ Notification

Refined Abstraction â†’ Alert, Reminder

Implementor â†’ NotificationSender

Concrete Implementor â†’ EmailSender, SMSSender


ğŸ”Ÿ Ratane Ka Tarika (Exam / Interview Trick)

Yaad rakhne ka formula:

WHAT + HOW = Bridge

Ya phir:

Feature alag, Functionality alag

Ya phir:

Abstraction holds reference of Implementor

